<h2>Newsletter  - May 7, 2019</h2>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan = 1 align = center bgcolor = #abacab height = 1></td></tr>
<tr>
<td class =body2 align = left>
We found a way to significantly decrease our monthly hosting cost - from almost $700/month to $150/month. This includes the total hosting for our all of our websites and customers websites. And even better, it will allow us to do a better job of offering benefits to our hosting customers. <br /><br />

We expect to complete the transition from our previous hosting solution to the new one within the next month.
<a href = "NewsletterApril5072019.asp" class = "body">...</a><br />
<img src = "/images/px.gif" width = 20 height = 1 /><a href = "NewsletterApril5072019.asp" class = "body2"><i>Read More</i></a><br /><br />

<b>Weekly Highlight - About Livestock Of America</b><br />
Livestock Of America (<a href = "https://www.LivestockOfamerica.com" class = "body" target = "_blank">www.LivestockOfAmerica.com</a>) is our first online marketplace and our current focus.
Our target audience is livestock businesses that generate between $1,000 and $250,000 / year. These businesses produce farm-fresh eggs for Huevos Rancheros that make your mouth sing; melt-in-your-mouth steaks that you can eat with a spoon; snuggly softest sweaters, and socks so warm that your tootsies will stay warm on Mt. Everest. And they do most of their business at farmers markets and by word of mouth ... and their profit margins stink.<br />

<img src = "/images/px.gif" width = 20 height = 1 /><a href = "NewsletterApril5072019.asp#Highlight" class= "body2"><i>Read More</i></a>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td class =body2 align = left><br />
<h2>Newsletter  - April 30, 2019</h2>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan = 1 align = center bgcolor = #abacab height = 1></td></tr>
<tr>
<td class =body2 align = left>
We will start the NewChip Business Accelerator (<a href = "https://www.newchip.com" class = "body" target = "_blank">www.newchip.com</a>) tomorrow, and we are very excited.
<a href = "NewsletterApril4302019.asp" class = "body">...</a><br />
<img src = "/images/px.gif" width = 20 height = 1 /><a href = "NewsletterApril4302019.asp" class = "body2"><i>Read More</i></a><br /><br />

<b>Weekly Highlight - Livestock Wiki</b><br />
We have compiled an extensive list of livestock breeds - over 2,000 breeds of Alpacas, Bison, Cattle, Chickens, Dogs, Donkeys, Emus, Goats, Bees, Horses, Llamas, Pigs, Rabbits, Sheep, Turkeys, and Yaks. So far we have researched and written over 1,000 descriptions (about 50%). This is a huge task and our plan is to complete it by crowdsourcing it and making it into a wiki.<br />

<img src = "/images/px.gif" width = 20 height = 1 /><a href = "NewsletterApril4302019.asp#Highlight" class= "body2"><i>Read More</i></a>
</td>
</tr>



